Tga '''Taruct''' zɣ tamsgza n imrmidn (قوارض). Ar ittuẓla (يتميز) [[Imudar|umudr]] ad s kigan n isnnan imsadn zun-d win [[Inikf|insi]] (bumḥnd) macc win taruct ɣzzifn uggar d tfkka ns ttugr tin insi, ar tn tswwuri afadd a ttmzaɣ (تدافع) f ixf ns zɣ imudar yaḍni. Tamurt ns taẓuṛant tlla ɣ Timrikiyyin, Asya, Tafriqt, Urupa. Tga tiss kṛaḍt imqqurn ɣ wanaw n imrmidn dffir n ilf n waman d [[Akbur|wanẓiḍ]] n waman (القندس). Ar tlkkm tiɣzi n taruct gr 64 d 91 cm, d tiɣzi n ucṭṭab ns gr 20 d 25 cm, d ar tlkkm tiɣzi n isnnan nns gr 60 d 70 cm ,  d taẓḍuyt ns gr 5,4 ar 15 kg. [[Aklu]] n taruct illa ɣ udmman (awras - aqhwi) d ublbac (رمادي) d usggan d idrus ma ɣ ayttgga umlil. 

Taruct tga zɣ imudar infradn (عاشب), ar tctta ifrawn n waddagn d tuga d iẓlan (أعصان) d immɣayn izgzawn zun-d akrus d ɣ tagrst ar tctta tifli (اللحاء). D tga zɣ imudar ittmussun ɣ yiḍ (ḍyyḍ) macc kra n tikkal ar ttmussu ula ɣ taylgi afadd attcubbu s tutca ns.
